new libraries being used

Update ResearchGPT.py

Significant reliability improvements. Additional features include:
1. The function that determines when enough research has been gathered on one search query or not now has the ability to give feedback and direction to the summary generator. Additionally, if the function does choose to continue on with the same query, it must now specify exactly what information is needed. This helps prevent it for continuing for the sake of continuing
Update ResearchGPT.py

Update ResearchGPT.py

Changes:
1) Increased the maximum number of google queries GPT-4 is allowed to make from 5 to 8
2) Text is now extracted from links for pdf and htm documents
3) Output is now saved to a Word document with proper formatting, which opens up as soon as the script is done running
4) Some prompt improvements to get more details from the website in summarization, a more detailed report, and additional reminders to GPT-4 to output only in JSON format
